### Checklist and Comments HTTP Tests
### These tests require a running server. Use against http://localhost:5000

### Replace {{token}} with a valid JWT or use the auth endpoint first.
### These are smoke tests for manual/API testing of all checklist and comment endpoints.

### ==========================================
### CHECKLIST ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Create a checklist item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
 "text": "Design the schema",
    "assignedTo": null,
    "position": null
}

### Create a checklist item with assignee
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "Implement the feature",
    "assignedTo": "{{userId}}",
    "position": null
}

### List checklist items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a checklist item
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist/{itemId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "Updated text for the item",
    "assignedTo": null
}

### Toggle a checklist item (mark complete/incomplete)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist/{itemId}/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reorder a checklist item
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist/{itemId}/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "newPosition": 0
}

### Delete a checklist item
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist/{itemId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### COMMENT ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Create a comment with mention
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "Hey @alice can you review this?"
}

### Create a plain comment
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "This looks good to me."
}

### List comments
GET http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a comment
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/comments/{commentId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "Updated comment content with @bob mention"
}

### Archive a comment (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/comments/{commentId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### ERROR CASES
### ==========================================

### Create checklist item - invalid assignee (non-member)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "Task",
    "assignedTo": "{{nonMemberId}}"
}

### Create checklist item - invalid position
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "Task",
    "position": 999
}

### Reorder checklist item - invalid position
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist/{itemId}/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "newPosition": 999
}

### Non-member access - all endpoints return 403
GET http://localhost:5000/api/projects/{projectId}/cards/{cardId}/checklist
Authorization: Bearer {{nonMemberToken}}